      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BOLT OF FUN (1) filled a minor placing last start at this track behind Sunset Chromium (22.47) in a Grade 4. Led around the bend before fighting on well and should give a sight. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and five minor placings to her credit. Can measure up this time. CLIFTON JASPER (3) was well back throughout but attacked the line strongly to place, 4 lengths from the winner (22.62) at this track in Free For All. Goes very well from this draw. Has a strong record out of this box with three wins and a minor placing from four starts. Ready to find winning form. PARADISE PARIS (7) has recorded back to back wins here, last time overcoming a bump to score over 400m by 1.3 lengths (22.49). Has the ability and looks a key chance. SHEERAN MELODY (2) can return to form after missing the top-three at this circuit last time out.",
